  "description": "Wraps an output and queues writes to process them asynchronously.\nUseful for file and network I/O to avoid blocking the main thread.\nAOT-compatible: Uses queuing and thread management, no reflection.",
  "title": "Class AsyncLogOutput",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Outputs_AsyncLogOutput'>Class AsyncLogOutput    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Outputs/AsyncLogOutput.cs#L41'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Wraps an output and queues writes to process them asynchronously.\nUseful for file and network I/O to avoid blocking the main thread.\nAOT-compatible: Uses queuing and thread management, no reflection.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class AsyncLogOutput : ILogOutput, IDisposable</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.html'>AsyncLogOutput</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Implements</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput.html'>ILogOutput</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.idisposable'>IDisposable</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.#ctor(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput,System.Int32)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.#ctor(Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput,System.Int32)' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Outputs_AsyncLogOutput__ctor_Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogOutput_System_Int32_'>AsyncLogOutput(ILogOutput, int)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Outputs/AsyncLogOutput.cs#L73'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the AsyncLogOutput class.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public AsyncLogOutput(ILogOutput innerOutput, int maxQueueSize = 10000)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>innerOutput</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogOutput.html'>ILogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The underlying output to wrap.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>maxQueueSize</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Out